  "texts": [
    "Concurrently, outdated tort liability laws may not adequately address AI's role in healthcare.",
    "This leads to compounded risks: the AI's misdiagnoses are exacerbated by unclear liabilities, heightening overall risk magnitude in patient care.",
    "AI risk can then compound with the risk of the digital infrastructure in which an AIs operates.",
    "Finally, AI risk can cascade into multiple other types of risk, the risk to innovation, to digital sovereignty, to economic sustainability, to power concentration, and so forth.",
    "This third stage of interaction should be linked to that of ancillary risks, i.e., risks posed or increased by the risk regulation itself."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}